bbcp (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Add Ubuntu 24.04 LTS support
  * Modernize build system and documentation
  * Full support for GCC 13 and OpenSSL 3.0
  * Cross-platform support: Linux, macOS, FreeBSD, AIX
  * Features:
    - High-speed parallel transfers using multiple TCP streams
    - Data integrity with MD5, CRC32, and Adler32 checksums
    - Built-in zlib compression
    - Real-time progress monitoring
    - Seamless SSH integration

 -- Carlos <cfpandrade@users.noreply.github.com>  Sun, 08 Dec 2024 21:29:00 -0500
